title: Consultation on future of early intervention services and children’s centres (Oxfordshire County Council)
text: ( Source : Oxfordshire County Council ) The council's cabinet decided at its September meeting to put three options out for consultation. The focus in the options is on protecting the most vulnerable children from abuse and neglect. People
